@QuantityMeasurementApp.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5097

### Signup
POST {{QuantityMeasurementApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "Test User",
	"email": "test.user@example.com",
	"password": "Test@123"
}

### Login
POST {{QuantityMeasurementApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "test.user@example.com",
	"password": "Test@123"
}

### Google Login (paste a valid Google ID token)
POST {{QuantityMeasurementApp.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"idToken": "PASTE_GOOGLE_ID_TOKEN_HERE"
}

###
